    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's make crepes on the Steam!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook with finesse, place the right toppings, and make as many crepes as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach for the ultimate high score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Rules》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook the batter and choose toppings to match the order!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work quickly and accurately for maximum points, and don't let your batter burn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep making crepes until time runs out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《How to Play》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Pour the batter and spread it out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. When the batter cooks, start adding the toppings listed in the order!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Add whipped cream or choco cream!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Add strawberries, kiwi, banana, or mango!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Add strawberry, kiwi, chocolate, or mango sauce!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. When your crepe is finished cooking, wrap it up! Your crepe is complete!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Score Attack】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make as many crepes as you can, and aim for a high spot on the leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Battle】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with others and test your crepe-making skills!</p>",
